 de ecologiepremie+ aanvraagt</a>.</p><p>De formele bevestiging van de toekenning van de subsidie gebeurt gemiddeld 2 maanden nadat je de aanvraag gedaan hebt. De beslissing wordt per brief meegedeeld. </p>","en":"<p>The application is made electronically on <a href=\"https://www.vlaio.be/nl/vlaio-netwerk/flanders-innovation-entrepreneurship/subsidies-entrepreneurs/subsidies-entrepreneurs#Ecology-Premium-Plus\">www.ecologiepremie.be</a>. In order to secure the personal data to a maximum extent, the entrepreneur must register by means of a federal token or an electronic identity card. An enterprise cannot have started the investments before the first day of the month following the month of the submission date of the ecology premium. The date of the first invoice counts as starting date. The ecological investments must be ended within 3 years following the decision to grant an ecological premium. The termination takes place on the date of the last invoice. Enterprises thus have three years to realise their environmental investments.</p>"},"@type":"Procedure","order":0}],"websites":[{"naam":{"nl":"Ecologiepremie+ (VLAIO.be)","nl-BE-x-formal":"Ecologiepremie+ (VLAIO.be)","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Ecologiepremie+ (VLAIO.be)","en-x-generated":"Ecology premium+ (VLAIO.be)"},"url":"https://www.vlaio.be/nl/subsidies-financiering/ecologiepremie","@type":"Website","order":0},{"naam":{"en":"Subsidies for entrepreneurs"},"url":"https://www.vlaio.be/nl/andere-doelgroepen/flanders-innovation-entrepreneurship/subsidies-entrepreneurs/subsidies","@type":"Website","order":1}],"financieleVoordelen":[{"beschrijving":{"nl":"<p>De ecologiepremie+ wordt toegekend in de vorm van een subsidie. Het bedrag wordt bepaald door:</p><ul><li>de aard van de investering</li><li>de ecoklasse waartoe een technologie behoort op basis van zijn ecologiegetal met corresponderend subsidiepercentage</li><li>de grootte van de onderneming.</li></ul><p><a href=\"https://www.vlaio.be/nl/subsidies-financierin